STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Asim Q. JULES, Defendant-Respondent. C-577 September Term 2017
079947 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 12, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002400-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted and the matter is summarily remanded to the Superior Court Appellate Division for reconsideration in light of A-85/86-16 State v. Evans , ___ N.J. ___ (2018). Jurisdiction is not retained.
